snippet.title: JumpStart Animal Adventures/Advanced Animal Field Trip
snippet.description:
Hey, how's it going? This is rescuehero942 here with my brand new high-quality gaming channel. I will be uploading gameplay of mostly forgotten kids computer and video games. Let's start off with an Animal Adventure, where CJ's nieces and nephews enter the JumpStart Animal Habitat Contest. This was a really fun entry in the JumpStart subjects series, but sadly, as far as my knowledge goes, footage has been lacking for this one.

JumpStart Animal Adventures is a personal computer game released in 2002. It teaches skills about nature, animals, and habitats for ages four and up. It was released in Great Britain as Frankie: Animal Adventures. It was also re-released as JumpStart Animal Field Trip in the JumpStart Advanced Kindergarten bundle starting in 2003.

It can be considered as something of a sister game to JumpStart Explorers, as both feature fairly similar features, the same main characters, and a focus on a particular subject. 

It was also released with Chick-fil-A Kids' Meals as part of a promotion.
